* example of Interactive Geant session.
* 
* To run this kumac type " exec SimulationMods/test/intGeant.kumac " from
* GEANT prompt.

message Example of Interactive Geant session.

* initialize memory
gr/opt zfl

* print all volumes mames
print volu 0

* show particular volume specification
dspec cdf

* plot cdf slice in z-y plane, x=0:
null -600 600 -600 600
dcut cdf 1 0 0 0 1 1

message For more options see geant manual.
message  
message  to print pictures - 
message        gr/opt zfl
message        pi/pr filename.ps 
message
message  after "dspec" volume will be highlighted
message  
message Bye!  